 />\n經濟再次起飛  唔好再搞亂香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你自己唔關心既野 就話人左癌<br />\n人地唔關心黃屍就話人地法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef23f38a79205e60edfb69af930a57643814565","tid":2248943,"uid":208674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"原本想借BLM黎用政治吸引人，之前有個非裔比人開槍咩都唔知就公鹿私自擺賽，重要停左差唔多成個星期，玩火玩到燒著自己，依家未轉軚話減少政治囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d6d9d02bf2e4711e1923a2907f9da9d206edf5","tid":2248943,"uid":67896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"希望仲可以見到呢個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThank you Matan Even<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZ4HrPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZ4HrPL.jpg&h=bb06abc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"accb348b310178fcd38fe597d7a5b24e8ac1e9d8","tid":2248943,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ef23f38a79205e60edfb69af930a57643814565","tid":2248943,"uid":208674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"原本想借BLM黎用政治吸引人，之前有個非裔比人開槍咩都唔知就公鹿私自擺賽，重要停左差唔多成個星期，玩火玩到燒著自己，依家未轉軚話減少政治囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"英超反而做得唔錯。開波前表態。球員唔會日日9up 加批鬥人"},{"pid":"95e3485da44b21053de707a291342e81e66e5138","tid":2248943,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"黑人有咩唔公平，靠高就賺咁多錢，<br />\n<br />\n少少野就話俾人歧視，<br />\n你不如留係非洲啦，<br />\n<br />\n非洲日日死黑人數，一定係白人世界過千倍，<br />\n非洲黑人等你班nba大帝去拯救呀"}]}